<seg id="227">The two parties agreed that the cooperation will focus on the following areas: (A) verification of the validity and correctness of the VAT registration numbers of persons registered for VAT in the Czech Republic and the Slovak Republic for intra-community supplies; (b) verification of data on intra-community purchases listed in the DAP by payers in the Czech Republic using information from summary reports (hereinafter referred to as "SH") of payers from the Slovak Republic contained in the VIES system, and vice versa; (c) exchange of information between tax administrations in the Czech Republic and the Slovak Republic on business transactions carried out.</seg>
