<seg id="940">Comparison</seg>
<seg id="941">The aim of EMCS was to replace a system based on paper-based transport administration.</seg>
<seg id="942">The benefits of EMCS are a comprehensive overview of transport between Member States within the EU, from the announcement of the start of transport to the end of transport, with a significant reduction in administrative costs for tax administrations and tax entities for processing, handing over and archiving documents.</seg>
